START.
SSS XY-1.
SSSS _Y.
SSSS Z.

MAIN.
PRINT "Please enter a number? ".
INPUT _Y.

MOVE 15 TO Z.
ADD Y TO Z.
PRINT XY-1;" + ";Y;"=";Z.

END.



